snippet.title: Jake Everest 2 Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on another epic match-3 journey with adventurer and archaeologist Jake Everest! After concluding his last adventure, Jake has once against returned to protect artifacts from those who would steal them. His latest endeavor leads him to find a mysterious object with ancient runes inscribed on it.

When he recognizes matching runes at the Gunung Padang archaeological site, he boards a plane to investigate the connection. There, his efforts alongside the archaeological team will lead them to discover lost secrets beyond anything they ever imagined.

Download the trial for your desktop!
https://www.bigfishgames.com/us/en/pc-games.html

Available for Game Club members on June 14th, 2023.

Try the original Jake Everest:
PC:
